$ Zero Data Loss Recovery Appliance
@ Recovery Appliance

*Recovery Appliance* offers protection for all → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database[Oracle databases] in an organization.

*Recovery Appliance* is integrated with → development/databases/Oracle/tools/Enterprise-Manager/Cloud-Control and → development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN.

→ development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/media-manager/Oracle-Secure-Backup is the tape management component of Recovery Appliance.

{ Installation

  In order to use Recover Appliance, it must be installed in the → Linux/fhs/u01/app/oracle/product/vv-v-v/dbhome_n[Oracle home directory] of the
  → development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/target-database.

}
